283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bafd78466e39fd620874a0fb329f95297ad0a92e","tid":1308301,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"日日示威好累架，1星期有5日和理非回下氣得唔得？"},{"pid":"25641fa39c5a936f5aa1f9fcca3b50b4fc6dfe0d","tid":1308301,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:09:49.000Z","msg":"屌見到大埔唱光輝歲月就諗起香蕉奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b063ca0acb9ecbc1a95245812c741b560c9351c","tid":1308301,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38c066faf94f8b03321674f3b2df6dd447928f0","tid":1308301,"uid":145423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75281823ce57ec5843d1c07a04a43a88bff46551","tid":1308301,"uid":100337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3e9143df317fbd87f50f4a5855b08777fba9a4a","tid":1308301,"uid":145423,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"